lead_paragraph: Midfielder Henrikh Mkhitaryan needs to put in more effort to move ahead of his rivals in the pecking order and prove he is worthy of a place in Manchester United's starting line-up, manager Jose Mourinho has said.

headline.print_headline: Mourinho Urges Mkhitaryan to Earn His Place in Side
headline.main: Mourinho Urges Mkhitaryan to Earn His Place in Side
